* Dunbar. 1987. &quot;Demography and Reproduction&quot;. In &quot;Primate Societies&quot;. Smuts, B.B., Cheney, D.L., Seyfarth, R.M., Wrangham, R.W., Struhsaker, T.T. (eds). Chicago &amp; London:University of Chicago Press. pp.¬†240‚Äì249 
* Dunbar. 1988. &quot;Primate Social Systems&quot;. Chapman Hall and Yale University Press 
