===M4 layout ‚Äì &quot;Rear Mid-engine / Four-wheel drive&quot;===

These cars use mid-ship, four-wheel-drive, with an engine between the axles.

*Ares Design Project1
*Audi R8
*BMW i8
*Bugatti EB 110, Veyron, Chiron, Divo, Centodieci
